      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BORN TO RAVISH (3) was well in the betting when resuming but only beat a couple home. Was trialling well prior and placed in his only previous attempt. Draws well and should be fitter so is worth another chance. STEELY ZAC (4) did a good job to come from the back row and finish third on debut at this circuit and distance. Steps out of maiden grade here but is open to natural improvement. LUCIENDO BIEN (11) started favourite on debut but broke so did well to recover for fourth. Cops a tough draw but has upside. LOCHINVAR COOGEE (7) will be fitter second up and draws for a trail. Can feature if he gets the gaps.",
